curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/8092' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2300", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM2300 is a high voltage and low power  consumption linear regulator. It is capable of supplying  50mA output current. The operating input voltage is up  to 18V. The output voltage range is from 1.5V to 5.0V in  fixed output version. For adjustable output version, the  output voltage can be adjusted from 1.5V to 5.0V by  using external resistors.  Other features include current limit and thermal  shutdown protection.  The SGM2300 is available in Green SOT-23 and  SOT-23-5 packages. It operates over an operating  temperature range of -40℃ to +85℃.  "}'
curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/8093' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2300", "table_name": "FEATURES", "content": "FEATURES   High Input Voltage: Up to 18V   Fixed Output Voltages: 1.5V, 1.8V, 2.5V, 2.8V, 3.0V,  3.3V, 3.6V and 5.0V   Adjustable Output Voltages: 1.5V to 5.0V   50mA Guaranteed Output Current   Output Voltage Accuracy: ±3% at +25℃   Low Dropout Voltage   Low Power Consumption: 1.7μA (TYP)   Low Temperature Coefficient   Thermal Shutdown Protection   Output Current Limit   -40℃ to +85℃ Operating Temperature Range   Available in Green SOT-23 and SOT-23-5 Packages    "}'
